Info.Title: Roseville
Info.Writer: Boby Zahariev (screenplay), Martin Makariev (story), Alexander Penev (story)
Info.Actors: David Chokachi, Lora Dekova, Lydia Indjova, Plamen Manassiev
Info.Plot: The events surrounding the unsolved police case in which guests of a mountain hut come face to face with terror, when the mysterious force that stalks them in the dark, violently knocks on the door of their consciousness.
